16 F. Failure to include any of the required disclosures under
17 this section shall render the contract invalid and unenforceable by
18 the wholesaler and shall entitle the homeowner to any earnest money
19 deposit involved in the transaction. Any earnest money deposit or
20 security deposit by a wholesaler shall be kept in an escrow account
21 maintained in this state with a federally insured financial
22 institution. The homeowner may terminate the contract at any time
23 if the wholesaler fails to comply with the provisions of this
24 section.
